bugs.fix:
Improve efficiency by using a set to track seen items and another set for duplicates, or by using a dictionary to count item frequencies. For example:
```python
def find_duplicates_efficient(data):
    seen = set()
    duplicates = set()
    for item in data:
        if item in seen:
            duplicates.add(item)
        else:
            seen.add(item)
    return list(duplicates)
```
